  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2020-1121<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2020-12-18</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nHer Excellency the Governor General in Council, on&nbsp;the recommendation of the Minister of Transport, pursuant to&nbsp;section 36 of the <em>Pilotage Act</em>,\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(a) repeals Order in Council P.C. 2020-33 of&nbsp;January&nbsp;30,&nbsp;2020; and\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(b) fixes the maximum amount of money that can be borrowed by the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, in Canada or&nbsp;elsewhere, for the purpose of defraying its expenses, at&nbsp;CAN $20 million.</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSur recommandation du ministre des Transports et&nbsp;en vertu de l’article 36 de la <em>Loi sur le pilotage</em>, Son Excellence la&nbsp;Gouverneure générale en conseil&nbsp;:\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\na) abroge le décret C.P. 2020-33 du 30 janvier 2020;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nb) fixe à 20&nbsp;000 000&nbsp;$ CAN le plafond des emprunts que l’Administration de pilotage de l’Atlantique peut contracter, au Canada ou ailleurs, pour pouvoir acquitter ses frais.\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
